@node Intro "Introduction"
@smartwrap


If you aren't familiar with music modules, you should first read the section
which explains @{"a bit about them" link AboutMods}.


If you are familiar with the MEDUtils package, you may want to read the
@{"release history" link History} for a summary of changes.


The MEDUtils package consists of a module player - @{"MEDPlay" link MEDPlay} - and a module
ripper - @{"MEDRip" link MEDRip} - plus a few extra bits of software to support them.


I wrote these programs after finding my existing module software inadequate. I
hope you find them as useful as I have. If you find these inadequate or
out-dated then I'm very sorry!


@endnode


